"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block war drugH1Div\" id=\"F232438\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Warnings/Precautions",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
